NESS (Navy Engineering Software System) is sponsoring a 
one-day Navy Scientific Visualization and Virtual Reality Seminar.  The
purpose of the seminar is to present and exchange information for
Navy-related scientific visualization and virtual reality programs, 
research, developments, and applications NESS?

Ness presentations are solicited on all aspects of 
Navy-related scientific visualization and virtual reality. All 
current work, works-in-progress, and proposed work by Navy 
organizations will be considered.  Four types of presentations are 
available.


